<h1># 🚀 Binance Futures Trading Bot (Testnet)<h1/>

<p align="center">
  <b>CLI + Streamlit + Docker + Logging</b><br>
  A modular trading bot for Binance Futures Testnet with a clean architecture and real-time UI.
</p>

